Package locations

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Location
    Provides an interface for locations that can be traveled to from the home base in the centre of the City
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    City
    Defines the Cities that the game is based around.
    DiceRoll
    This is a game called Dice Roll, roll a higher number to win Numbers range from 1-6 and it is best out three games
    GuessANumber
    This is a game called Guess a Number, guess the correct number to win Numbers range from 1-10 and it is best out three games
    Hospital
    A location that allows HealingItems to be applied to a Hero
    Lair
    A location that incorporates a Villain.
    PaperScissorsRock
    This is a game called Paper Scissors Rock, rock beats scissors, scissors beats paper and paper beats rock 3 Options to choose from, paper scissors or rock
    PowerUpDen
    Allows heroes to use haggling booster and illusion booster
    Shop
    Provides a way for heroes to purchase power ups and healing items
    VillainGame
    Provides an interface for a game that can be played in a Villains Lair
